# 개발 표준 및 코딩 컨벤션

## 네이밍 규칙

### 파일명
```
Screen: [도메인]Screen.tsx      예) OrderListScreen.tsx
Step:   Step[N][기능].tsx       예) Step1Info.tsx, Step2ServiceSelection.tsx
Flow:   [도메인]FlowScreen.tsx  예) OrderFlowScreen.tsx
Service: mock[도메인]Data.ts    예) mockCustomerService.ts
```

### 컴포넌트/함수
```typescript
// ✅ GOOD
const OrderListScreen: React.FC = () => { ... }
const handleSubmit = () => { ... }
const isValidPhone = (phone: string): boolean => { ... }

// ❌ BAD
const orderlist = () => { ... }
const Submit = () => { ... }
```

### 상수/타입
```typescript
// ✅ GOOD
type StepStatus = 'PENDING' | 'ACTIVE' | 'COMPLETED' | 'WARNING';
const MAX_STEPS = 6;

// ❌ BAD
type stepstatus = 'pending' | 'active';
```

